Name: worker_task_assignment
Description: Boolean assignment of a worker to a task.

Name: feature_sprint_assignment
Description: Which sprint a feature is assigned to.

Name: story_point_estimate
Description: The estimated story points for a User Story.

Name: team_size
Description: The number of workers assigned to a team.

Name: sprint_goal_priority
Description: Priority level of the sprint goal.

Name: task_sequence_order
Description: The order in which tasks are to be completed.

Name: skill_requirement_level
Description: The required proficiency level of a skill for a task.

Name: meeting_duration_min
Description: The allocated duration for a ceremony in minutes.

Name: worker_availability_pct
Description: The percentage of time a worker is available in a sprint.

Name: budget_allocation
Description: The amount of budget allocated to a specific feature.

Name: blocker_resolution_sprint
Description: The sprint in which a blocker is targeted to be resolved.
